summer games in Seoul, Korea.

138
00:08:27,740 --> 00:08:32,006
- W-Wait. You're Derice Bannock, right?
- That's me.

139
00:08:32,078 --> 00:08:34,273
Oh. I hope I make the team.

140
00:08:34,347 --> 00:08:36,645
It would be a real honor
to run with you.

141
00:08:36,716 --> 00:08:38,741
- Good luck to you.
- Good luck to you.

142
00:08:38,818 --> 00:08:43,278
