He's an American who lives here.

161
00:10:37,336 --> 00:10:39,964
Unless, of course,
he's been arrested or shot.

162
00:10:40,039 --> 00:10:43,133
- Excuse me?
- Well, he's a bookie now.

163
00:10:43,209 --> 00:10:46,770
