just past Sandy Bay.

164
00:10:46,846 --> 00:10:48,871
Isn't that a gold medal
around his neck?

165
00:10:48,948 --> 00:10:52,008
Oh, yeah. That lunatic
was an Olympic bobsledder...

166
00:10:52,084 --> 00:10:55,485
