170
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:11,931
- And you sure this man,
he lives on the island?
- Oh, yes.

171
00:11:12,004 --> 00:11:14,802
- Mr. Coolidge, thanks a lot.
- Good, Derice.

172
00:11:14,874 --> 00:11:18,435
- Oh. Could I borrow this picture?
- Bring it back.

173
