But you said no, and that's all right
because I don't need ya.

196
00:12:38,958 --> 00:12:42,587
Everybody is gonna want to be
on my bobsled team.

197
00:12:42,661 --> 00:12:45,960
Look, star, let me tell you
a little somethin', all right?

198
